  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing the Portal\'s Foundation**\n\nI\'m focusing on the EMBER Youth Leader Portal\'s website. It requires a truly responsive design that seamlessly adapts to mobile, tablet, and desktop viewports. My current task is to meticulously analyze the images and HTML code provided to inform the initial design. I\'m aiming for both functionality and aesthetic appeal.\n\n\n**Defining the Platform\'s Core**\n\nI\'ve outlined the essential modules: the EMBER dashboard with key metrics; a content and prayer hub for moderation; a live attendance scanner; an announcement system; a youth member directory; and an events console. Each has core functions like data display, and active modules. The modules will be integrated within the same system. I am focusing on seamless connectivity.\n\n\n**Assessing the Tech Stack**\n\nI\'m now determining the optimal tech stack for the EMBER portal. After reviewing the features, I\'m verifying available skills, like cloud SQL and Firebase. I aim to create a design that aligns with the skills I have, so I must start from what is available. I will integrate the features as seamless components within the responsive website.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will read `package.json` to inspect the project scripts and structure."
    thinking_duration {
