  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Elegant Dark\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Elegant Dark\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#09090b] text-slate-200 font-sans p-12 flex flex-col overflow-hidden select-none\\\"><header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end border-b border-white/10 pb-8 mb-12\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-1\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-4xl font-extralight tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-white\\\">Omnia <span class=\\\"font-black text-emerald-500\\\">Framework</span></h1><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500/60 font-mono tracking-[0.5em] uppercase\\\">Unified Design Language // Phase 4</p></div><div class=\\\"text-right flex flex-col items-end gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/30\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/30\\\"></div></div><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono\\\">STABLE_BUILD: 2024.10.12</p></div></header><main class=\\\"flex-1 relative flex items-center justify-center\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[580px] h-[400px] bg-[#18181b] rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden z-10 flex flex-col\\\"><div class=\\\"h-8 bg-[#27272a] border-b border-white/5 flex items-center px-4 gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/40\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/40\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/40\\\"></div><div class=\\\"ml-4 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">https://omnia-framework.io</div></div><div class=\\\"p-10 flex flex-col h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#18181b] to-[#09090b]\\\"><nav class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-12\\\"><div class=\\\"text-sm font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">OMNIA</div><div class=\\\"flex gap-6 text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-medium\\\"><span>System</span><span>Nodes</span><span>Archive</span></div></nav><div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-5xl font-light leading-tight text-white\\\">Architecture for <br/><span class=\\\"italic font-serif text-emerald-400\\\">Tomorrow</span></h2><p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 max-w-[320px] leading-relaxed\\\">A hyper-responsive engine that recalibrates digital experiences for the next generation of hardware.</p><div class=\\\"pt-8 flex gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-emerald-600 text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm\\\">Initialize</div><div class=\\\"px-6 py-2 border border-white/20 text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm\\\">Documentation</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\\\"absolute left-[540px] top-[140px] w-[240px] h-[340px] bg-[#18181b] rounded-[32px] border-[8px] border-[#27272a] shadow-2xl z-20 overflow-hidden flex flex-col shadow-black/80\\\"><div class=\\\"p-6 flex flex-col h-full bg-[#111113]\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-8\\\"><div class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold\\\">OMNIA</div><div class=\\\"w-4 h-3 flex flex-col justify-between py-0.5\\\"><div class=\\\"h-[1px] bg-white w-full\\\"></div><div class=\\\"h-[1px] bg-white w-2/3\\\"></div></div></div><h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-light mb-6 text-white\\\">Seamless <br/>Sync</h3><div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\"><div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full bg-emerald-500/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full w-3/4 bg-emerald-500\\\"></div></div><div class=\\\"h-12 bg-white/5 border border-white/5 rounded-lg\\\"></div><div class=\\\"h-12 bg-white/5 border border-white/5 rounded-lg\\\"></div></div><div class=\\\"mt-auto\\\"><button class=\\\"w-full py-2.5 bg-emerald-600/20 border border-emerald-500/30 text-emerald-400 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase rounded-lg\\\">Activate Tablet</button></div></div></div><div class=\\\"absolute right-[80px] bottom-[120px] w-[130px] h-[260px] bg-[#09090b] rounded-[24px] border-[4px] border-[#27272a] shadow-2xl z-30 overflow-hidden flex flex-col shadow-black/90\\\"><div class=\\\"h-4 w-12 bg-[#27272a] rounded-b-lg mx-auto\\\"></div><div class=\\\"p-4 flex flex-col h-full items-center text-center\\\"><div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mt-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full\\\"></div></div><h4 class=\\\"text-[11px] font-medium text-white mb-2\\\">Mobile <br/>Refiner</h4><p class=\\\"text-[8px] text-slate-500 mb-6\\\">Touch-optimized core logic.</p><div class=\\\"w-full space-y-2\\\"><div class=\\\"h-8 bg-white/5 rounded-md\\\"></div><div class=\\\"h-8 bg-emerald-600 rounded-md\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"h-1 w-10 bg-white/10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-full\\\"></div></div></main><footer class=\\\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-12 border-t border-white/10 pt-10\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic\\\">01. Desktop Edge</p><p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 leading-normal\\\">Full-scale immersive environment with high-precision grid control and layout density.</p></div><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic\\\">02. Tablet Core</p><p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 leading-normal\\\">Adaptive intermediate state preserving hierarchy while simplifying navigation for touch interaction.</p></div><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic\\\">03. Mobile Micro</p><p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 leading-normal\\\">Condensed functional architecture designed for vertical scanning and one-handed engagement.</p></div><div class=\\\"flex justify-end items-center text-right\\\"><div class=\\\"font-mono text-[9px] text-slate-600 space-y-0.5\\\"><div>RENDER_ENGINE: ACTIVE</div><div>VIEWPORT_STRATEGY: FLUID</div><div>COMPLIANCE: AAA_WCAG</div></div></div></footer></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Elegant Dark\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Elegant Dark\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#09090b] text-slate-200 font-sans p-12 flex flex-col overflow-hidden select-none\\\"><header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end border-b border-white/10 pb-8 mb-12\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-1\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-4xl font-extralight tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-white\\\">Omnia <span class=\\\"font-black text-emerald-500\\\">Framework</span></h1><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500/60 font-mono tracking-[0.5em] uppercase\\\">Unified Design Language // Phase 4</p></div><div class=\\\"text-right flex flex-col items-end gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/30\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/30\\\"></div></div><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono\\\">STABLE_BUILD: 2024.10.12</p></div></header><main class=\\\"flex-1 relative flex items-center justify-center\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[580px] h-[400px] bg-[#18181b] rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden z-10 flex flex-col\\\"><div class=\\\"h-8 bg-[#27272a] border-b border-white/5 flex items-center px-4 gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/40\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/40\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/40\\\"></div><div class=\\\"ml-4 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">https://omnia-framework.io</div></div><div class=\\\"p-10 flex flex-col h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#18181b] to-[#09090b]\\\"><nav class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-12\\\"><div class=\\\"text-sm font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">OMNIA</div><div class=\\\"flex gap-6 text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-medium\\\"><span>System</span><span>Nodes</span><span>Archive</span></div></nav><div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-5xl font-light leading-tight text-white\\\">Architecture for <br/><span class=\\\"italic font-serif text-emerald-400\\\">Tomorrow</span></h2><p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 max-w-[320px] leading-relaxed\\\">A hyper-responsive engine that recalibrates digital experiences for the next generation of hardware.</p><div class=\\\"pt-8 flex gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-emerald-600 text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm\\\">Initialize</div><div class=\\\"px-6 py-2 border border-white/20 text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm\\\">Documentation</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\\\"absolute left-[540px] top-[140px] w-[240px] h-[340px] bg-[#18181b] rounded-[32px] border-[8px] border-[#27272a] shadow-2xl z-20 overflow-hidden flex flex-col shadow-black/80\\\"><div class=\\\"p-6 flex flex-col h-full bg-[#111113]\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-8\\\"><div class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold\\\">OMNIA</div><div class=\\\"w-4 h-3 flex flex-col justify-between py-0.5\\\"><div class=\\\"h-[1px] bg-white w-full\\\"></div><div class=\\\"h-[1px] bg-white w-2/3\\\"></div></div></div><h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-light mb-6 text-white\\\">Seamless <br/>Sync</h3><div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\"><div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full bg-emerald-500/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full w-3/4 bg-emerald-500\\\"></div></div><div class=\\\"h-12 bg-white/5 border border-white/5 rounded-lg\\\"></div><div class=\\\"h-12 bg-white/5 border border-white/5 rounded-lg\\\"></div></div><div class=\\\"mt-auto\\\"><button class=\\\"w-full py-2.5 bg-emerald-600/20 border border-emerald-500/30 text-emerald-400 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase rounded-lg\\\">Activate Tablet</button></div></div></div><div class=\\\"absolute right-[80px] bottom-[120px] w-[130px] h-[260px] bg-[#09090b] rounded-[24px] border-[4px] border-[#27272a] shadow-2xl z-30 overflow-hidden flex flex-col shadow-black/90\\\"><div class=\\\"h-4 w-12 bg-[#27272a] rounded-b-lg mx-auto\\\"></div><div class=\\\"p-4 flex flex-col h-full items-center text-center\\\"><div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mt-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full\\\"></div></div><h4 class=\\\"text-[11px] font-medium text-white mb-2\\\">Mobile <br/>Refiner</h4><p class=\\\"text-[8px] text-slate-500 mb-6\\\">Touch-optimized core logic.</p><div class=\\\"w-full space-y-2\\\"><div class=\\\"h-8 bg-white/5 rounded-md\\\"></div><div class=\\\"h-8 bg-emerald-600 rounded-md\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"h-1 w-10 bg-white/10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-full\\\"></div></div></main><footer class=\\\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-12 border-t border-white/10 pt-10\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic\\\">01. Desktop Edge</p><p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 leading-normal\\\">Full-scale immersive environment with high-precision grid control and layout density.</p></div><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic\\\">02. Tablet Core</p><p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 leading-normal\\\">Adaptive intermediate state preserving hierarchy while simplifying navigation for touch interaction.</p></div><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic\\\">03. Mobile Micro</p><p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 leading-normal\\\">Condensed functional architecture designed for vertical scanning and one-handed engagement.</p></div><div class=\\\"flex justify-end items-center text-right\\\"><div class=\\\"font-mono text-[9px] text-slate-600 space-y-0.5\\\"><div>RENDER_ENGINE: ACTIVE</div><div>VIEWPORT_STRATEGY: FLUID</div><div>COMPLIANCE: AAA_WCAG</div></div></div></footer></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
  }
}
