  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Confirming Implementation**\n\nI\'m pleased to report a flawless linting and compilation process! The \"Elegant Dark\" visual theme has been perfectly applied to the application. I have decided to revisit the user request and related metadata.\n\n\n**Refining Style Integration**\n\nI\'ve carefully extracted the styling and layout patterns from the design. I\'ve focused on precisely mapping the \"Elegant Dark\" theme\'s aesthetics to the existing application structure. Specifically, I\'ve redefined the `@theme` palette in `src/index.css` to align with the elegant dark colors. I\'m focusing on preserving functionality while ensuring the theme\'s visual fidelity.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have successfully applied the **Elegant Dark** design theme to the **Ember Youth Leader Portal**, aligning all colors, gradients, shadows, borders, scrollbars, and typography details to match the aesthetics of the modern zinc-and-emerald design guidelines.\n\n### Design Concept Breakdown\n\nHere is a summary of the styling updates applied to transition the applet to the **Elegant Dark** design system:\n\n*   **Zinc & Charcoal Foundations**: Redefined core surface system tokens inside `src/index.css` to map to deep zinc tones (background canvas at pure black-zinc `#09090b`, inner modules, containers, and card layers spanning `#111113`, `#18181b`, and `#27272a`).\n*   **Emerald & Teal Accents**: Swapped out legacy warm orange highlights for vibrant, tech-forward emerald signals (Primary `#10b981`, Secondary `#34d399`, and deep forest indicators `#047857`/`#059669`). This coordinates seamlessly with existing alert states, attendance badges, check-in buttons, and scan laser lines.\n*   **High-Contrast Minimal Borders**: Adjusted the global `outline-variant` and dividers to use elegant translucent borders (`rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)`), matching the thin structural rules of the design template.\n*   **Polished Sidebar Branding**: Upgraded the portal header branding in `Sidebar.tsx` to utilize an ultra-light tracking layout:\n    *   **Ember Portal Title**: Re-styled to a premium `\"Ember Portal\"` heading (`text-lg font-extralight tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-white` paired with a bold emerald highlight).\n    *   **System Subtitle**: Set to a monospaced indicator (`\"YOUTH_SYSTEM // PH_4\"` in a tiny `tracking-[0.3em]` uppercase style) to reflect the digital aesthetic.\n*   **Unified UI Components & Micro-Animations**:\n    *   **Glass Panel & Cards**: Overhauled glass backdrops to blend dark translucent bases with emerald border hover highlights.\n    *   **Attendance Scanning Laser**: Calibrated the vertical check-in scanner pulse shadow from legacy yellow to high-contrast emerald (`#10b981`).\n    *   **Micro-Interaction Scrollbars**: Upgraded thumb hovers to high-response emerald-500 indicators.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 3
      nanos: 426385994
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
